sources.title: San Andreas Quake | Full Action Adventure Movie | Disaster Survival
sources.description:
San Andreas Quake - When a discredited L.A. Seismologist warns of an impending 12.7 earthquake, no one takes her seriously. Now on her own, she races desperately to get her family to safety before the earthquake breaks Los Angeles apart from the mainland.

2015. Stars: Jhey Castles, Jason Woods, Grace Van Dien
